my workflow Development Process From idea to tangible working software. Lets Begin
Strategy Questions First. Before starting to write code i always make sure that we understand whatever we are trying to accomplish by asking the rights questions. This stage entails meetings, competitive analysis, solutions exploration and requirements gathering Design Problem Solving. At the end of this phase you will have a clear idea of what the application will look like, the processes involved, users targeted. I take the questions asked and turn them to Strategy Developement. This i my best part as we now get to work. With clear requirements in hand i am eager to materialize your idea into its tangible equivalent. Strategy Quality Assuarance. In this phase i present you with the final product over coffee. We test the functionality of the system with some of your users and determine wheather it addresses their needs.
